What does this mean for Chrisitans in China?

6
00:00:17,520 --> 00:00:18,480
Welcome to China Uncensored.

7
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:19,560
I'm Chris Chappell.

8
00:00:19,560 --> 00:00:22,039
