51
00:03:14,060 --> 00:03:24,629
You see, before this agreement between Vatican
and Chinese government,

52
00:03:24,629 --> 00:03:28,900
in several places like in Hubei,

53
00:03:28,900 --> 00:03:38,209
in Sensi, in Fouken, in Wenzhou,

54
00:03:38,209 --> 00:03:43,390
they have churches, buildings for the underground.

55
00:03:43,390 --> 00:03:48,740
